---
title: Chicken over Creamy Parmesan Couscous with Roasted Carrots
description: This luscious and foolproof charmer of a meal should do the trick when it comes to impressing the new boo or bae, maybe even nudge them over that relationship line? What we’ve got here is a creamy, cheesy, velvety bed of bouncy couscous lovingly showered with Parmesan. You’ll top that with Italian-seasoned pork chops seared to juicy golden brown perfection. And on the side we’ve got simple salt and pepper roasted carrots. Sprinkle with scallion greens for a pop of color and flavor just before serving, and we guarantee your date will be putty in your hands!
